        "content": "<p>Thank you <span class=\"user-mention\" data-user-id=\"314358\">@Donald Sebastian Leung</span>  that's actually my first successful use of <code>by_contra</code>:</p>\n<div class=\"codehilite\" data-code-language=\"Lean\"><pre><span></span><code><span class=\"kd\">theorem</span> <span class=\"n\">negneg</span> <span class=\"o\">(</span><span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"kt\">Prop</span><span class=\"o\">)</span> <span class=\"o\">:</span> <span class=\"bp\">¬¬</span><span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"bp\">→</span> <span class=\"n\">p</span> <span class=\"o\">:=</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">begin</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">intro</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">by_contra</span> <span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n  <span class=\"n\">exact</span> <span class=\"n\">h</span> <span class=\"n\">h1</span><span class=\"o\">,</span>\n<span class=\"kd\">end</span>\n</code></pre></div>",
